      "raw": "<table class=\"my_table_border\">\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: none;\">\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"3\">\n                                ćwiartka III\n                            </td>\n<td colspan=\"3\">\n                                ćwiartka IV\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\alpha\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(210^{\\circ}\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(225^{\\circ}\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(240^{\\circ}\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(300^{\\circ}\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(315^{\\circ}\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(330^{\\circ}\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\cos\\alpha\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(-\\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(-\\frac{\\sqrt{2}}{2}\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(-\\frac{1}{2}\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\frac{1}{2}\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\frac{\\sqrt{2}}{2}\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n                                \\(\\sin\\alpha\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(-\\frac{1}{2}\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(-\\frac{\\sqrt{2}}{2}\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(-\\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(-\\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(-\\frac{\\sqrt{2}}{2}\\)\n                            </td>\n<td>\n                                \\(-\\frac{1}{2}\\)\n                            </td>\n</tr>\n</table>",
      "reason": "table uses rowspan/colspan"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<p>\n                Obliczenie tangensa lub cotangensa wymaga jeszcze jednego działania:\n            </p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<ul class=\"nolist\">\n<li>\n                    \\(\\text{tg}\\alpha=\\frac{\\sin\\alpha}{\\cos\\alpha}=\\frac{y}{x}\\)\n                </li>\n<li>\n                    \\(\\text{ctg}\\alpha=\\frac{\\cos\\alpha}{\\sin\\alpha}=\\frac{x}{y}\\)\n                </li>\n</ul>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<p>\n                Ponieważ dla tych kątów mianowniki sinusów i cosinusów są równe \\(2\\), dla uzyskania tanensa i cotangensa wystarczy podzielić liczniki.\n            </p>"
    }
